kdl.prox.model2.rdn
Class RPTTableCacher

java.lang.Object
  kdl.prox.model2.rdn.RPTTableCacher

public class RPTTableCacher
extends java.lang.Object

This utility class maps the RPT's class labels to temporary attributes, and re-maps the learned feature settings in each RPT's to use those temporary attributes.

When done, cleanup() restores the original feature settings and removes the created attributes.
